body_html:
Looks like this is an issue caused by centos 6.9
A quick google search found these similar issues, and potential solution here:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17150075/undefined-reference-to-clock-gettime-although-lrt-is-given

Closing, as this issue is definitely caused by OS version of the user.
